Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.43,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\frz-90\pos(475,432)\c&H1A1F28&\fad(500,0)}一里波知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天起终于成为初中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来人消灭掉学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,新的朋友 新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,孤零零一个人的初中生活开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:06.12,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\c&HA66EF1&\pos(1782.412,803.769)}初次{\fs40\c&H9FA144&}的{\r\c&HA66EF1&}告白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要升学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小学九年制不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要问我为什么这么不想升到初中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不擅长与人交往的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和唯一的朋友说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 波知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不一样初中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:00.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\frz-90\c&H1A1F28&\pos(386.48,544.2)\fad(500,0)}八原香依（从小认识）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要努力交到不一样的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,波知在初中毕业之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在和全班同学成为朋友之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不会不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我约定好 交好多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来跟我和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,香依
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,送你这个加油妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,香依 这样的我要去交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不行的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不交朋友也能达成约定的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,初中消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,失败
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,其二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个作战可能能行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,约定的是和全班都成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟班级的大小无关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,同班同学是0个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以说跟全班都是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,1班怎么看人都很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以希望不是1班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要是1班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要是1…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,1班了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,29个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里真让人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在可不是干这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,开学典礼刚刚结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有人来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让大家全都转走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一里波知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,和这里大家都成为朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这贴的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,1班废除？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谁的恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,犯罪了吗 会被抓住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看来会是个很有意思的班级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,1班废除诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要变成超级1班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,超有干劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看来1班的人很有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不如说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我还挺怕生的 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,班级的人好像很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很怕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,作战其三也失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说更加团结了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,香依 我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,作战其四
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,四是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,人类都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是半夜的情绪写的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,遵守约定要跟香依和好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的 我相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为波知从来没有打破约定过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,香依
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,香依 没有一时冲动说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这笔记有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,约定的是和全班都成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还是只能加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,打开这扇门 大声打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,首先从这个开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在门口就打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只有电视剧里看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我很怕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人也和我一样怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那还是不要搭话比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次见到就那么近呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人和我不一样 一点都不怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那还是不要搭话比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,各种人都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,外国人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,砂尾同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,开学典礼也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,从自我介绍开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫美奈川来羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢班级里开开心心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要交朋友 第一次自我介绍很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,相当的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫砂尾菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\frz-90\c&H1A1F28&\fad(500,0)\pos(1586.584,516.115)}砂尾菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,开朗点 开朗点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一里同学
Comment: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,===============
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,自我介绍还是太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和人说话都像是拷问一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先和座位前面的搭话看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,砂尾同学 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不过先搭话试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,脚抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,休息5秒之后就去搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,超过5了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 呕吐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呕吐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不过比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是多久没有过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和同年龄的人对话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,砂尾同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,太奶奶说对喉咙好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,叫谁奶奶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你想当跑腿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,跑腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是很懂这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,去找其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,跑腿算朋友的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和砂尾同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不知道该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来和香依和好也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是砂尾同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你想当跑腿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,明天开始上课了 大家好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.65,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没带伞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请用我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是跑腿的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只是砂尾同学在咳嗽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只会恶化 这不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你这话怎么讲的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,逃跑了 逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,香依 我没法遵守约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,砂尾同学是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,能好好跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 呕吐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,都叫你等下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,砂尾同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你神色那么夸张挥舞着伞就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,的确 是这样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一把伞的话 一起撑就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个是还你果汁的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,砂尾同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我菜子就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说想交朋友我也挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要在意什么奇怪的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 波知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,交朋友的诀窍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就是喜欢上对面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的话要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,聊天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要聊天 首先要从精神的打招呼开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,精神 精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你突然干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,想要精神点跟你打招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让你离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那难道说是被讨厌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 你在误会什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你要打招呼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得空虚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为了这种时候 我做了日常对话的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子一直在玩手机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要开始什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏不在选项里 能跳过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是你想问什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怎么用手机的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我没什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是想交换邮箱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这个选项能不能跳过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,说了的吧 不用顾虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 有想说的就讲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那 可以的话能告诉我邮箱地址吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,回家就去死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,说点什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 要多说点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要多说点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请说点有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吃什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,甜的 不喜欢辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子发消息的时候语气都不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想像菜子那样加点图
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,颜文字？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,点颜文字转换就行了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,全身？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,放学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也就早上好好对话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别边走路边用手机了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,用手机说话真开心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,手机回家再说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那喜欢吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,又是这选项吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的问题第二遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还要继续的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有是有的 但是保密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有的 但是保密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好像喜欢上了菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以能做我朋友 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说你还觉得不是朋友的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你还没有同意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真是有点怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那么怪 那么笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那么老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我没能好好说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,总是说奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说你怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我觉得这就是你好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不说清楚就不明白的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就是OK的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天就已经这样了吧 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是进了初中第一次和朋友一起回家是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天也是一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天还没有和朋友一起回家的心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,心理准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说的是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是想对谁说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,除我之外没人能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,走咯 波知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,新的朋友 新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的初中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了
Comment: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,========OP========
